dc_title_s: Miami Beach - Section One - Lower Twp., Cape May County, N.J.
dc_description_s: Map covers area between Jacksonville Ave. and Schellinger Ave. and between Ormond Rd. and the Delaware Bay in Lower Township, New Jersey. Map is attached to map of Miami Beach - Section Two - Lower Twp., Cape May County, N.J.. It shows roads and real estate lots in the area.
